  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the family was split.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she was taken away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she had-- she didn't know what her uncle's name was or where he was living.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I decided to do something about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was no civilian mail at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So through the Army Post Office, I wrote to the chairman or president of the Zionist Federation of Australia and gave him the story and asked him what he could do to locate this man.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had no name, no first name, nothing-- didn't even know the name of the-- oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We did know the names of the-- Sophie's parents, yeah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he wrote back that-- this, this whole thing took quite several months, during which time Sophie was looked after by these friends of mine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And eventually, I had a letter back from the-- from Australia to say that the only thing they could do there would be to advertise in the with whatever information was available and see what came out of it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
